description.en: YIN Finance is a multi-strategy NFT liquidity management platform that allows users to subscribe to the project’s strategies (CHIs) to achieve effective high-yield liquidity management on different public chains and decentralized exchanges. In addition to CHI, there is the native platform token $YIN, as well as an NFT Vault to be released named YANG, and leveraged yield farming in their GRAND MASTER module.
